		<h2 id="section1" style="color:mediumspringgreen;">Introduction</h2>
		<p>
			With the continuous development of Internet technology and the popularity of smart products, Cyber Security has increasingly become the focus of attention.Cybersecurity is the practice of protecting critical systems and sensitive information from digital attacks. Also known as information technology (IT) security, cybersecurity measures are designed to combat threats against networked systems and applications, whether those threats originate from inside or outside of an organization.
			<p>When we use smart products, we are often subject to different types of security threats, whether stealing customer account records or clicking on a <strong>phishing link, suspicious activity by employees,Vendors and suppliers</strong> (or malware that learns to imitate insider behavior while quietly exfiltrating data may cause property damage or privacy leakage. Therefore, software that comes with smart product systems, software developed by third-party companies, and a large amount of network security education have become popular. , related discussions often occur on Twitter.

