		<p> I have collected 3823 pieces of information about Cyber Security, and there are many official and well-known Twitter users who initiated this hashtag. It surprises me that there is a lot of information about EVs as well as autonomous driving in the discussion about cybersecurity.</p>

		<h4>(a) The top tweeters and retweeters</h4>
		<p> <strong>Top ten twitter</strong>: ___L__A___, corqtrade, CyberSecurityN8, embedded_house, sectest9, SK_Expert, Zxcxz_xyz, jamesvgingerich, SemonesRandy, uCloudify.</p>
