    <p> <strong>Top ten retwitter</strong> BlackBerry, business_today, DainikBhaskar, IndiaToday, jamesvgingerich, moneycontrolcom, rahulkanwal, Telegraph, TimesNow, WSJJapan. TimeNow has the most followers about 20,636,596 followers, and he mentioned the current situation of Renault and Tesla in the text. At the same time, other 9 main users under the topic of Cyber Security also mentioned EV-related information.</p>
