	 <p>After my screening, I found 2 bots in top10 twitterï¼Œ the first is ___L__A___,  it sent 16.9K tweets, but only 466 followers. During this period of time, he sent a lot of repeated messages about Cyber Security and EV, which rarely received replies or likes.</p>
