    <p>The data of my data set comes from Twitters released from 08Jan-11Jan. From the perspective of Demographic, these Twitters mainly come from industrially developed countries such as India, England, and Canada, and the number of tweets reached its peak in 09Jan.Similar to the database as a whole, "EV" and "Tesla" were the focus of discussion. This method can be applied to study the changes in the industry and the focus of the discussion.
